        <p>If you intend to use micro content in your HTML5 output search results, you need to make sure it is enabled in the target.</p>
        <div class="video" MadCap:conditions="General.Server-Only">
            <p class="buttonT32-play"><a href="https://youtu.be/_AAqTsa0WCM" data-lity="true" class="buttonT32-play-link">WATCH&#160;THE&#160;VIDEO</a>
