            </p>
        </div>
        <h2>How to Enable Micro Content</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Open an HTML5 target.</li>
            <li>Select the <span class="Emphasis">Search</span> tab.</li>
            <li>From the <span class="Emphasis">Search Engine</span> section, make sure <span class="Emphasis">MadCap Search</span> or <span class="Emphasis">Elasticsearch</span> is selected.</li>
            <li>Expand the <span class="Emphasis">Advanced Search Options</span> section.</li>
            <li>Select <span class="Emphasis">Include micro contents results</span>.</li>
            <li>
                <MadCap:snippetText src="../../../Shared/All/General/Save-File.flsnp" />
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
